body:
### [Current repositories](https://github.com/dpmcmlxxvi)

Name  | Description
----- | -------------
[clistats](https://github.com/dpmcmlxxvi/clistats) | C++ application to compute statistics for a stream of input numbers
[clitestbed](https://github.com/dpmcmlxxvi/clitestbed) | C++ application test bed to run a suite of tests on a program
[olexp](https://github.com/dpmcmlxxvi/olexp) | Javascript library that combines OpenLayers with the w2ui layout manager
[pixelscan](https://github.com/dpmcmlxxvi/pixelscan) | Python library to scan pixels on a grid in a variety of spatial patterns
